menu "Focus Pager"

config PAGER_SIMULATOR
    bool "Simulator build (disables Bluetooth for Wokwi)"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, all Bluetooth initialisation (BT controller,
        Bluedroid, ANCS, HFP, brick service) is skipped so the
        firmware can run in the Wokwi simulator without panicking.
        Only the display, encoder, and NVS store are active.

endmenu
